---
const rocket = './../../public/icons/rocket.svg';
const graph = './../../public/icons/graph.svg';
---
<style>

  @media screen and (max-width: 1180px) {
    #waitCard-top {
      right: auto;
    }

    #waitCard-bottom {
      left: auto;
      text-align: left;
    }
  }
</style>

<div class="bg-[#F7F2FF] px-4 pt-6 pb-12 m-auto">
  <div class="text-center font-semobold text-gray-800 py-4">
    <h3 class="font-semibold pb-4">How the <span class="bg-gradient-to-r from-red-500 to-orange-500 bg-clip-text text-transparent font-bold">ScamAi SUPER Quantum Automation</span> Tool Works</h3>
  </div>

  <div class="grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 md:grid-cols-3 md:gap-2 gap-4 lg:gap-10 container m-auto pb-4">
    <div class="bg-[#FFE7B3] p-4 rounded border border-white h-full">
      <div class="text-center pb-2">
        <div class="bg-gradient-to-b from-indigo-500 to-pink-500 rounded-full absolute w-12 h-12 mt-[-34px] ml-[-32px]">
          <p class="font-bold text-4xl p-0 m-0 pt-1 text-white">1</p>
        </div>
        <h3 class="text-[#FFB71D]">INITIATE</h3>
      </div>

      <div class="flex flex-row">
        <div class="border border-4 border-[#5E51ED] bg-white rounded w-full h-10 mr-2"></div>
        <button class="bg-[#5E51ED] rounded px-4 w-20"><img src={rocket} /></button>
      </div>

      <div class="border border-[#CEC5C5] shadow-md bg-white h-fit rounded my-2 max-w-full md:max-w-[263px]">
        <ul class="px-4 py-2 text-gray-800">
          <li class="pb-2 pt-2 mb-2 border-b border-gray-400"><p>1. Upload your processes.</p></li>
          <li class="pb-2 mb-2 border-b border-gray-400"><p>2. Explain your needs.</p></li>
          <li class="pb-2 mb-2 border-b border-gray-400"><p>3. Grant access to all company tools.</p></li>
          <li class="pb-2 mb-2 border-b border-gray-400"><p>4. Sign our NDA.</p></li>
          <li class="pb-2 mb-2"><p>5. Pay us $$$$.</p></li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="bg-[#AEDCFD] p-4 rounded border border-white h-full flex flex-col">
      <div class="text-center pb-2">
        <div class="bg-gradient-to-r from-red-500 to-orange-500 rounded-full absolute w-12 h-12 mt-[-34px] ml-[-32px]">
          <p class="font-bold text-4xl p-0 m-0 pt-1 text-white">2</p>
        </div>
        <h3 class="text-[#37ABFF]">WAIT</h3>
      </div>

      <div class="flex flex-col h-full justify-between text-gray-800">
        <div class="bg-white flex-grow mb-6 rounded-md px-4 pb-2 pt-4 shadow relative md:right-10" id="waitCard-top">
          <h4 class="font-semibold ">Brainstorm, then build.</h4>
          <p class="font-light text-base py-2">Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consectetur adipiscing elit. Vivamus finibus dictum purus at laoreet. </p>
        </div>
  
        <div class="text-right bg-white flex-grow rounded-md px-4 pb-2 pt-4 shadow relative md:left-10" id="waitCard-bottom">
          <h4 class="font-semibold">Automate. Everything.</h4>
          <p class="font-light text-base py-2">Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consectetur adipiscing elit. Vivamus finibus dictum purus at laoreet. </p>
        </div>
      </div>

    </div>

    <div class="bg-[#F6B4CF] p-4 rounded border border-white h-full flex flex-col text-gray-800 max-h-fit">
      <div class="text-center pb-2">
        <div class="bg-gradient-to-r from-emerald-500 to-lime-600 rounded-full absolute w-12 h-12 mt-[-34px] ml-[-32px]">
          <p class="font-bold text-4xl p-0 m-0 pt-1 text-white">3</p>
        </div>
        <h3 class="text-[#FF4C95]">PROFIT</h3>
      </div>

      <div class="bg-white h-fit rounded justify-between flex flex-col h-full shadow">
        <div class="px-4">
          <h4 class="text-left pt-4 pb-2 font-bold">See the Results.</h4>
          <p class="font-light text-base">ScamAi curates a bespoke software based on your company structure and processes to fit your company needs to scam your clients faster!</p>
        </div>

        <div class="p-4 flex flex-col mb-0 pb-0">
          <div class="w-full m-auto relative">
            <img src={graph} class="m-auto w-[200px] pb-4" />
          </div>
        </div>
        
      </div>
    </div>

  </div>
</div>